Keyboard bindings:
------------------

    S                =>    Save to permanent-folder
    R                =>    Recover from auto-save
    L                =>    Load last saved from temporary folder

    Escape           =>    Shut down
    BackSpace        =>    Clear messages
    Space            =>    Reset scene
    Home             =>    Place view back to start

Gesture Colors:
---------------

    Grabbing         =>    Yellow                    => move
    Dual-grabbing    =>    Blue                      => zoom/rotate
    Picking          =>    Green : picked vertex     => select/deselect
                           Red   : picked nothing    => nothing
